Date: 16/3/2000
Source: Dominion
Author:
Vol / Page: 2
Edition:
Quote: [Hdg] Dak and ruin amid mass inhalations.... New Zealand First's Ron Mark suggested that, since the Government was happy to back compulsory testing of police and defence personnel, it should set an example by introducing compulsory drug-testing of MPs and staff. "Or are we to allow Parliament to go to dak and ruin", he added., mystifying more innocent members with his pun on one of the many cool slang names for marijuana.
