Date: 1/4/2000
Source: Listener (New Zealand Listener)
Author:
Vol / Page: 58
Edition:
Quote: So, when Ron Mark MP suggested drug testing our elected representatives in the wake of the latest joint-spotted-in-House brouhaha - memorably punning a threat of things going "to dak and ruin" in the process - it was unclear to an irony-challenged individual like myself whether he was serious.
